videos.description: Ja Morant gets crafty around the rim with an up-and-under layup.
videos.headline: Morant goes up and under for a lay-in

videos.description: Malik Dunbar doesn't give up a on fast break as he chases down the ball and swats it off the backboard.
videos.headline: Dunbar gets a chase-down block

videos.description: Ja Morant finishes a fast break by throwing down a big slam.
videos.headline: Morant gets a steal and caps off fast break with a huge dunk

videos.description: Chuma Okeke gets a running start for a putback dunk on Murray State defenders.
videos.headline: Okeke rises up for putback slam in traffic

videos.description: Ja Morant gets by an Auburn double team to throw a lob for Shaq Buchanan, who goes up high to throw down it down.
videos.headline: Morant crosses 2 defenders, throws lob to Buchanan for slam

videos.description: Jared Harper gets by Ja Morant and throws a dime to Samir Doughty, who knocks in a 3-pointer to give Auburn a lead over Murray State.
videos.headline: Harper finds Doughty in the corner for an open 3

videos.description: Ja Morant is able to score on a floater and "rocks the baby" in the celebration.
videos.headline: Morant scores on Harper and 'rocks the baby'

videos.description: Ja Morant hangs it up high for Shaq Buchanan to catch and throw down.
videos.headline: Buchanan throws down alley-oop slam
